        <div class="desc">An open-source starting point for creating &amp; distributing static websites and <a href="https://ghost.org">Ghost</a> themes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="project four columns">
        <div class="title"><a href="https://github.com/jadnco/Plum" title="Plum">Plum</a></div>
        <div class="stack">Node, Express, Mongo, Ember</div>
        <div class="desc">An award-winning stock portfolio simulator in the works – for the next generation of investors.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="project four columns">
        <div class="title"><a href="http://darrenplace.com" title="Darren Place">Darren Place</a></div>
        <div class="stack">HTML, Sass</div>
        <div class="desc">A single page portfolio showcasing the work of a young visual effects artist based in Winnipeg, Canada.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="project four columns">
        <div class="title"><a href="https://github.com/jadnco/prattle" title="Prattle">Prattle</a></div>
        <div class="stack">HTML, CSS, PHP</div>
        <div class="desc">An asynchronous chatting application used for communicating with my fellow nerd-minded friends.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="project four columns">
        <div class="title"><a href="https://github.com/jadnco/sockets-pong" title="Pong">Pong</a></div>
        <div class="stack">Node, Socket.io, P5, EJS</div>
        <div class="desc">A re-make of the classical game with wireless multiplayer functionality – thanks to WebSockets.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="project four columns">
        <div class="title"><a href="https://github.com/jadnco/showcase" title="Showcase">Showcase</a></div>
        <div class="stack">HTML, CSS, PHP</div>
        <div class="desc">A customizable visual collection of your greatest projects linking out to Dribbble and Behance.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

